{"tid":701540,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有興趣創業（小食）","createTime":"2018-06-14T08:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T05:15:30.000Z","uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"616c175d729d911ddbf9ec08cfb4b8b869c5e783","tid":701540,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"15-20萬係一定要架啦（牌費/裝修/去水位/工具）<br />\n想搵1，2個人一齊夾 大家各自賣自己既野 <br />\n分租分鋪形式 詳細既再一齊傾<br />\n利潤賺蝕都係自己負責 <br />\n<br />\n或者你想拎個經驗咩都好 承諾做半年到一年左右 大家再傾 <br />\n（萬一做得兩個月你唔做 租果到我食哂 好撚大獲）<br />\n<br />\n我自己就想開返屯元天區 最好都係同區啦<br />\n如果你有其他意見 覺得邊到好既歡迎再傾"},{"pid":"fd1514b0e296157a1ec278e42b1123f0362c2748","tid":701540,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"屯元天區 等執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b691a3242076ee25853afcac04ae158c7faa69","tid":701540,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1514b0e296157a1ec278e42b1123f0362c2748","tid":701540,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"屯元天區 等執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"街坊生意 有咩問題？"},{"pid":"b33f0f0059e610ff8963925eee5b548a8b12d530","tid":701540,"uid":24632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"賣燒蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b17f438f9ac7d04853786c9b5aa6b272a90e6df","tid":701540,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b33f0f0059e610ff8963925eee5b548a8b12d530","tid":701540,"uid":24632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"賣燒蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我自己想做章魚燒 冷面之類"},{"pid